  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together flour, cornstarch, baking powder, salt, and sugar.",
    "Add grated coconut, onion, and beaten eggs to the bowl. Mix until well combined.",
    "Add milk and mix until the batter is smooth.",
    "Heat oil in a deep frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Using a spoon, drop small balls of the batter into the hot oil.",
    "Fry the fritters until they are golden brown, about 2-3 minutes on each side.",
    "Drain the fritters on paper towels and serve hot.",
    "Optional: Dust with additional flour for extra crunch."
  ],
